      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW INFLAME (8) jumped from this box and scored a Grade 5 win at Sale over 435m latest (24.54). Has a very consistent record off this same draw, including two and three places from eight starts. Rates a top chance again. LEKTRA HOPPER (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Mt Gambier in a handy 17.90 beating Pressure Point. Can make it back-to-back wins. PAW KARA (6) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (22.88) at Shepparton in a Grade 5 NP. Well placed here and can atone this time. INTUITIVE (2) is worth some thought after a surprise placing last start.",
